 <title>Accessible Information Guide to Direct Payment</title>
 <link>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/resources/accessible-information-guide-direct-payment</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-who field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Who is it for?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The Accessible Information Guide to Direct Payment is for anyone seeking to understand or support understanding of SDS option 1.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;What does it do?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Accessible Information Guide to Direct Payment explains how SDS option 1 works using short, easy read sentences and associated visuals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-how field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;How can you use it?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The Accessible Information Guide to Direct Payment is designed for use as a supplement to your verbal explanation of SDS option 1. You can record any questions the person asks and the answers you give in the space at the end of the guide. You can then leave the guide with the person for reference.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
